{"tid":1704424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黎明行動］致世界：看清楚了，我們只示範一次。","createTime":"2019-11-10T16:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:09:23.000Z","uid":266269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d51e156c425eaec38928d874b97038773ef82762","tid":1704424,"uid":266269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lU4JlG0ebUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlU4JlG0ebUY&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=9905a0b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lU4JlG0ebUY</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n梁繼平：「我們整個公民社會，會有十年永不翻身。我們的學生會被捕。我們的領袖會被捕。所以我們今次，要贏就要一起贏。<br />\n<br />\n我地已經失去得太多太多<br />\n要團結相信彼此<br />\n做法不完美 但可接受 要改善<br />\n條路只會愈黎愈難行，但係我地真係冇得再輸！<br />\n有幸同你地一齊經歷<br />\n此生無悔<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港🇭🇰"},{"pid":"068f0eddfc07f13cc6801363f8c843217b28acab","tid":1704424,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搭巴士有落千其要記得撳鐘<br />\n唔撳鐘巴士司機係唔會埋站㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外駕駛人士請注意</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DJ0kNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DJ0kNC.png&h=09b514a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AHPYzi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AHPYzi.jpg&h=91dc0471&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}